Fix richdem's Array2D.hpp to compile against modern GDAL (>= 3.7),
where GDALDataset::GetMetadata returns CSLConstList (const char* const*)
rather than char**.

Apply against
`submodules/dephier/submodules/richdem/include/richdem/common/Array2D.hpp`
in a local checkout of Barnes2020-FillSpillMerge. Do NOT push upstream.

  cd <FSM_CPP>/submodules/dephier/submodules/richdem
  git apply <FSM_Julia>/tools/patches/richdem-gdal-cslconstlist.patch

